{"title":"世纪颂","authors":["刘征"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":2,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪洪钟撼世声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢歌如海写豪情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开碧血江山丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风扫阴霾玉宇清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指日神州辉满月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂云大翼起高鹏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岱宗试向明朝望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔地参天未了青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1999年12月31日夜，在首都各界迎接新千年和新世纪活动上，一千名少年儿童朗诵了这首诗。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}